      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need help writing a rejection email for a candidate. they made it to the final round for a senior dev role here in austin but we decided to go with someone else. they were actually really good and had great technical skills, so i want the email to be professional and kind but still clear that we aren't moving forward. can u help me draft something?",
