      "content": "thanks for this. it's a good start but it feels a little too generic/standard. could you try to make it feel a bit more personalized? like, maybe add a sentence or two acknowledging that they were a top tier candidate and that the decision was actually really difficult for the hiring team because of how much we liked their background. just want to make sure they don't feel like it was a canned response.",
